R

register() - Static method in class gofoo.UserInterface
A function responsible for allowing the user to register as new player or a new playground owner and take the user personal information in both cases and if the user chooses to register as a player it will show him a sub menu whether to search for a playground by the number of hours wanted and then request to book it if he want or return to the main menu, and another sub menu if the user chooses to register as a playground owner which gives him the options to add a playground, view the requests for his playground or return back to the main menu.
Request - Class in gofoo
A class responsible for creating a request to book a play ground which aggregates with class Structure when the user as a player chooses to request a playground.
